               RP Category Balance Definition - Help

     Used to define the balance information requirements.  This
     information is accessed when a category code is specified
     in the Combined Category Code field on MICM panel 7101 (RP
     Model Definition) or in the Primary Category Code,
     Related Balance Category Code 1 or Related Balance Category
     Code 2 fields on MICM panel 7102 (RP Product Definition).






